OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fshowers. Most places will remain dry
OL,7,Fand showers will be lighter than
OL,8,Frecent days, though the odd heavy one
OL,9,Fmay still be possible. Winds on the
OL,10,Flight side, so feeling pleasant in the
OL,11,Fsunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FTurning wet from the
OL,14,Fsouthwest this evening, with the rain
OL,15,Fturning particularly heavy overnight,
OL,16,Fthough clearer spells moving into the
OL,17,Fwest towards dawn. Windy, with gales
OL,18,Fpossible for a time.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
