OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA wet and windy morning, but
OL,6,Fbrightening up during the afternoon
OL,7,Fwith a mixture of sunshine and
OL,8,Fshowers. Showers turning heavy, with
OL,9,Fpossible hail and thunder in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,12,Fbright start Sunday, but cloud
OL,13,Fgradually increasing through the day,
OL,14,Fwith rain overnight. Rain slowly
OL,15,Fclearing to sunny spells later Monday.
OL,16,FSunshine and showers following for
OL,17,FTuesday. Average temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
